('GYM_STREET_P2', 'Gym', 'Street', 1, '', 'Flat lay collage, editorial lookbook card on white background, neatly arranged product cut-out menswear items: black oversized sleeveless hoodie, baggy shorts with contrast piping, high-top training shoes, bold crew socks; clean editorial spacing, balanced negative space, subtle soft shadows, high-end product photography, ultra-sharp detail, minimal branding, no people, no mannequin --ar 4:5 --v 6 --style raw --s 150 --q 1', ' ', 'Oversized sleeveless hoodie taps into NYC’s gym-street crossover trend; urban volume styling layered over functional sports fabrics; street-casual blend suited for transitional weather.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
