('GYM_DANDY_P1', 'Gym', 'Dandy', 1, '', 'Flat lay collage, editorial lookbook card on eggshell background, neatly arranged product cut-out menswear items: fitted white performance polo, tailored black knit gym shorts, sleek white trainers, minimal performance pouch; clean editorial spacing, balanced negative space, subtle soft shadows, high-end product photography, ultra-sharp detail, minimal branding, no people, no mannequin --ar 4:5 --v 6 --style raw --s 150 --q 1', ' ', 'Refined polo set references NYC’s refined tech-knit preppy gym trend; breathable knit offers elegance with movement; balanced layering for early-year temperatures.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('GYM_DANDY_P2', 'Gym', 'Dandy', 1, '', 'Flat lay collage, editorial lookbook card on eggshell background, neatly arranged product cut-out menswear items: fitted black performance henley, tapered charcoal pants, crisp white minimal runners, slim socks; clean editorial spacing, balanced negative space, subtle soft shadows, high-end product photography, ultra-sharp detail, minimal branding, no people, no mannequin --ar 4:5 --v 6 --style raw --s 150 --q 1', ' ', 'Henley top and tailored joggers embody NYC’s smart athletic tailoring trend; ideal for gym professionals; maintains warmth without bulk under 10°C conditions.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('GYM_DANDY_P3', 'Gym', 'Dandy', 1, '', 'Flat lay collage, editorial lookbook card on eggshell background, neatly arranged product cut-out menswear items: soft knit performance tee, tailored joggers, neutral sneakers, thin socks; clean editorial spacing, balanced negative space, subtle soft shadows, high-end product photography, ultra-sharp detail, minimal branding, no people, no mannequin --ar 4:5 --v 6 --style raw --s 150 --q 1', ' ', 'Soft knit pieces reflect NYC’s 2026 elevated athletic knitwear trend; offers premium feel and mobility for gym settings; layering suitable for indoor warmth during cold season.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('GYM_SPORTY_P1', 'Gym', 'Sporty', 1, '', 'Flat lay collage, editorial lookbook card on white background, neatly arranged product cut-out menswear items: high-support performance tank, black shorts with racing stripes, performance running shoes, sport socks; clean editorial spacing, balanced negative space, subtle soft shadows, high-end product photography, ultra-sharp detail, minimal branding, no people, no mannequin --ar 4:5 --v 6 --style raw --s 150 --q 1', ' ', 'Dynamic racing-stripe look captures NYC’s activewear stripe revival trend; performance materials maintain comfort; tank design ideal for heated indoor workouts.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('GYM_SPORTY_P2', 'Gym', 'Sporty', 1, '', 'Flat lay collage, editorial lookbook card on white background, neatly arranged product cut-out menswear items: fitted moisture-wick tee, stretch leggings layered under shorts, cushioning trainers, no-show socks; clean editorial spacing, balanced negative space, subtle soft shadows, high-end product photography, ultra-sharp detail, minimal branding, no people, no mannequin --ar 4:5 --v 6 --style raw --s 150 --q 1', ' ', 'Layered leggings and shorts highlight NYC’s tech-layer performance trend; streamlined and warm for winter gym conditions; functional versatility for all training types.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('GYM_SPORTY_P3', 'Gym', 'Sporty', 1, '', 'Flat lay collage, editorial lookbook card on white background, neatly arranged product cut-out menswear items: cropped performance top, tapered grid-texture pants, flexible sole trainers, ankle socks; clean editorial spacing, balanced negative space, subtle soft shadows, high-end product photography, ultra-sharp detail, minimal branding, no people, no mannequin --ar 4:5 --v 6 --style raw --s 150 --q 1', ' ', 'Grid-textured tech pants embody NYC’s tech-athletic evolution trend; cropped top silhouette adds progressive sporty appeal; practical warmth for 8–5°C training environments.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '')
